{"tid":856380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗住幫政府籌一萬億？","createTime":"2018-10-10T14:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T14:30:44.000Z","uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba753fb2aa7a7f5252a66d4a2539e0215dd0b253","tid":856380,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"始終一萬億唔係個細數，遲啲政府應該都要加返個幾萬億落去。<br />\n我作為良好守法市民，真係好擔心政府唔夠錢用。好彩我喺屋企收埋左十五萬以備不時之需，陣間喺天地銀行應該都㩒到幾億出嚟捐俾政府。<br />\n有冇人同我一樣想幫政府出一分力？"},{"pid":"1826676c5c318987609d6a3517ad5cf78238a414","tid":856380,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"好似日本咁收消費稅"},{"pid":"9724e8e4a40f916be58f281833cf856e36ab9388","tid":856380,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n我地庫有幾千萬億 隨時可以送比政府 你地用哂問我再攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29c0ac7ff08dfdca8520ddccd07c8e860693ae3","tid":856380,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1826676c5c318987609d6a3517ad5cf78238a414","tid":856380,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"好似日本咁收消費稅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"我直接捐俾政府重快啦"},{"pid":"90c4ae850769ba6faa6ea8061fcc6f0ade6ac036","tid":856380,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"9dab95713fc8db75f7cab3b2be026389d66e5dda","tid":856380,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9724e8e4a40f916be58f281833cf856e36ab9388","tid":856380,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n我地庫有幾千萬億 隨時可以送比政府 你地用哂問我再攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:28:23.000Z","msg":"唉本身喺屋企放住十五萬就係想得閒買下中環，簿扶林啲地皮。見政府咁等錢洗唯有捐左先啦"},{"pid":"1ae0048517153e8481ec537210e6847e0bcfb677","ti